name: AlphabetGame
0:
”Alexa, start the alphabet game”
”D is the fourth letter”
”Tell me about D”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: alphabet game
des: This skill tests how well you know the alphabet. You can play a short game to give the location of a letter in the alphabet. Example: What is the location of D? You would reply " D is fourth"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
